    <span class="cit type-translation quote">they offered me the chance to work for them</span>
   </div>
   <div class="cit type-example">
    <span class="quote">¿cuánto te ofrecieron por el coche?</span> 
    <span class="cit type-translation quote">how much did they offer you for the car?</span>
   </div>
