    <span class="form type-phr orth">ofrecer hacer algo</span> 
    <span class="cit type-translation quote">to offer to do sth</span>
    <div class="cit type-example">
     <span class="quote">el club le ha ofrecido prorrogar su contrato</span> 
     <span class="cit type-translation quote">the club has offered to extend his contract</span>
